26 Nov 2024 navsp1  MTN-33493 NSW | OnePort Integration - Strip Spaces from Voyage Codes Provided
03 Dec 2024 navsp1  JIRA 33536 NSW - Oneport - Getting a 1090 when trying to load a Cancel message
05 Dec 2024	navmd1	MTN-33527 Include pre-transformed message on EDI file
14 Feb 2025 navsp1  JIRA-34037 NSW | Invoice Line not Generated for Voyage Resource
11 Mar 2025 navsp1  JIRA-34249 NSW | OnePort - Arrival Date Not Populated from Existing Voyage
14 Mar 2025 navsp1  JIRA-34340 NSW | 34310.010 OnePort Integration Voyage Creation
27 Mar 2025	naviv1	JIRA-34486 NSW - Voyage status is different on Voyage Enquiry and Voyage Definition for voyages created by OnePort message
28 Nov 2025 navsp1  MTN-35997 OnePort API update causing data issue- updated Arrival record after voyage closed
*/
constants
